      "text": "わぁ……東京の神社はこんなに人がいるんですね\n星見市の神社よりもずっと大きいし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… There are so many people at the shrine in Tokyo.\nIt's much bigger than the shrine in Hoshimi City…",
