      "text": "出店も沢山あるから、ゆっくり見て回ろうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are also many stalls‚ shall we take our time and look around?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7995237033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
