      "text": "琴乃？\nさっきからTシャツを見てるけど、気になるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono?\nYou've been looking at that T-shirt for a while‚ is something bothering you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "生活も仕事もずっと一緒だったからだと思うんですけど\n最近、月ストのみんなの影響を\n受けている気がするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's because we've been together in both our daily lives and work.\nLately‚ I feel like I've been influenced by\nthe Moon Tempest members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 44.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "Tシャツのドーナツから変な猫が顔を出している絵が\nなんだか可愛い……ような……気がします……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The picture of the donut on the T-shirt with a strange cat peeking out…\nIt somehow feels cute…?",
        "id": ""
