      "text": "なんで疑問形なんだ……\nとりあえず、芽衣と沙季の影響を受けてるのは分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you speaking in a questioning tone…?\nAnyway‚ I understand that you've been influenced by Mei and Saki.",
