      "text": "私、アイドルになった頃は、自分をお姉ちゃんや\nライバルのアイドルと比べてばかりいたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I first became an idol‚\nI was always comparing myself to my older sister and rival idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 118.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
