      "text": "それはだんだん落ち着いてきて……そしたら今度は\n星見のみんなと比べるようになってきたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gradually‚ I've become more calm…\nBut now I find myself comparing myself to everyone in Hoshimi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 128.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_02-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "特に月ストのみんなはずっと一緒にいるから余計に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially the Moon Tempest members‚ since we've been together for so long…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
